snippet.title: Fire Emblem: The Binding Blade :: Chapter 1 :: Dawn of Destiny
snippet.description:
A new blind journey through FE6 Hard Mode, let the suffering begin!

Fire Emblem (The Binding Blade/Sword of Seals/Fūin no Tsurugi) is the 6th Fire Emblem game in the franchise and was the first Fire Emblem game on the Gameboy Advanced, but was never released outside of Japan. to be localized and brought to the west. It was released in 2002 and features Roy and Lilina, the children of Eliwood and Hector of Fire Emblem: Blazing Sword, as they try to stop King Zephiel of Bern from conquering the continent of Elibe!

Weapon Art by Kynim:
deviantArt: http://ky-nim.deviantart.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/kyleenim
Tumblr: http://kynimdraws.tumblr.com/

Intro music - Winning Road (Roy's Hope) from Super Smash Bros. Brawl: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQiQ5NnYQds

Translation Patch: http://serenesforest.net/forums/index.php?showtopic=41095&p=2457854

Played on the VBA emulator.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discord: https://discord.gg/x8uMbM6
Twitter: https://twitter.com/poledoo
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/poledoo
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Please leave a like if you enjoyed :)
